Package: rleops
Title: Efficient Operations on Run Length Encoded Vectors
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Michal", "Piechota", email = "michalpiechotaa13@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Operations on Run-Length-Encoded vectors, that preserve the
    encoding of inputs and outputs. The library features basic binary operations,
    aggregations, running statistics and other handful utils.
